title: Did Russia Use Dart Frog Poison To Kill Opposition Leader Alexei Navalny? | 10 News+
description: Russia has long been accused of using exotic poison to eliminate its opponents.   But now there's claims the Kremlin weaponised a toxin found in the skin of a dart frog, to murder outspoken dissident Alexei Navalny.   The poison, which is called Epibatidine, is said to be 100 times more lethal than morphine.
